Copyright (c) 2024 Carlos Eduardo Braga

This software and educational material were developed exclusively for educational purposes as part of the Systems Development course at CentroWeg, Class MIDS 77, during the Programming Logic curricular unit, under the guidance of specialized teachers and with contributions and assistance from other teachers.

## Granted Permissions

- Anyone may view, copy, or fork this code and material for personal or educational purposes.
- It is allowed to study, learn from, and use it as a reference for personal programming development.
- Running the code as provided in this repository is permitted.
- Reproduction of exercises and algorithms for educational purposes is permitted.
- Use of concepts and methodologies mentioned in the projects is permitted.
- Use of flowcharts and diagrams for teaching purposes is permitted.

## Restrictions

- Direct modification of this code and redistribution as the original is not allowed.
- Changes may only be made in personal copies or forks, provided the reference to the original code and author is preserved.
- Commercial use is prohibited without the express permission of the author.
- Use of projects for malicious purposes or that may cause damage is not permitted.
- Exercises and algorithms must be reproduced responsibly and following educational practices.

## Educational Warnings

- Projects contain fundamental programming concepts that should be studied with dedication.
- Always test algorithms before applying them to real projects.
- Use good programming and documentation practices.
- Work in an organized environment with focus on learning.
- For projects with complex data structures, use adequate validations.

