The software and educational material are provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.

In no event shall the author, teachers, or the institution be liable for any claim, damages, or other liability arising from, out of, or in connection with the software and educational material or their use, including damages of any nature.

